    public interface EEFHyperlinkStyle
extends EEFWidgetStyle
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Hyperlink Style'. Represents a style that can be applied on hyperlink widgets.

    The following features are supported:

    • Background Color Expression
    • Font Name Expression
    • Font Size Expression
    • Font Style Expression
